### 3. SMARTPREX.COM ANALYSIS

#### 3A. Site Structure and Categories

Smartprix (https://www.smartprix.com/) is India's leading consumer tech comparison platform. Based on research:

**Primary Categories**:
- Mobiles (largest section)
- Tablets
- Laptops
- TVs
- Electronics (cameras, speakers, wearables)
- Appliances
- Automobiles

