|-----------------|------------------|
| **Brand** | Samsung, OnePlus, Apple, Motorola, Xiaomi, Vivo, Oppo, Realme, Poco, etc. |
| **Price** | Under 10K, 10-15K, 15-20K, 20-30K, 30-50K, Above 50K (and custom range) |
