#### 3C. Smartprix UX Patterns Worth Adopting

| Pattern | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Spec Score** | Computed score (0-100) based on all specifications -- helps users compare at a glance |
| **URL-based filters** | Filters encoded in URL path (e.g., `/mobiles/3_gb_above-ram?sort=spec_score`) for SEO and shareability |
| **Quick-filter chips** | Pre-built filter combos ("Best Camera Phones", "5G Phones Under 20K") as clickable cards |
| **Price history** | Shows price trend graphs for each product |
| **Side-by-side comparison** | Up to 4 phones compared with spec-by-spec table |
| **Pros/Cons summaries** | Quick bullet-point evaluations |
| **Last updated date** | Prominently shown to build trust |

